          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2478Step-3-1637330208994-x1500.jpeg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has caramelised, add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong>, <strong>curry powder</strong> and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until fragrant</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> tomato paste</strong> and<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
