    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>stock</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for 15 min or until the potatoes are fork-tender</p><p>Whilst the potatoes are cooking, wash your <strong>spring greens </strong>then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Rip the leaves off the <strong>spring greens</strong>, discard the tough stalks, then layer the leaves over each other, roll them up and slice into thin strips</p>",
