      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>basa fillet[s] </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Place the<strong> chopped basa </strong>over the curry and cook, covered, for 4-5 min or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
