      "instruction": "<p>To serve, lay the <strong>pie lid</strong> over the <strong>basa</strong> <strong>curry pie filling</strong> – this is your <strong>basa curry pie</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>basa curry pie</strong> with the <strong>mustardy greens</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
